00:29:54.040 --> 00:29:56.840
So the last couple
of years, we've

00:29:56.840 --> 00:29:59.200
been doing some
research on dishonesty.

00:29:59.200 --> 00:30:01.325
Actually, for many years,
we've been doing research

00:30:01.325 --> 00:30:01.908
on dishonesty.

00:30:01.908 --> 00:30:04.540
But we did a documentary
on dishonesty.

00:30:04.540 --> 00:30:08.050
And Noel Biderman that was
the CEO of Ashley Madison

00:30:08.050 --> 00:30:13.570
before this happened, was one
of the people we interviewed.

00:30:13.570 --> 00:30:18.380
And he actually had some
interesting observations

00:30:18.380 --> 00:30:21.450
