00:31:01.110 --> 00:31:03.450
Men, stereotypically,
don't do it.

00:31:03.450 --> 00:31:04.940
We talk about sports.

00:31:04.940 --> 00:31:07.110
But talking about
relationships actually

00:31:07.110 --> 00:31:10.370
helps you change your
relationship or improve things.

00:31:10.370 --> 00:31:15.720
Talking about sports doesn't
really help in that regard.

00:31:15.720 --> 00:31:19.680
And what Noel said
