ratio of men to women?

00:32:32.030 --> 00:32:34.160
In which type of
countries is the number

00:32:34.160 --> 00:32:36.460
more equal, and in
which countries there

00:32:36.460 --> 00:32:39.314
are more men and fewer women?

00:32:39.314 --> 00:32:40.480
What does it correlate with?

00:32:40.480 --> 00:32:41.396
What would you expect?

00:32:41.396 --> 00:32:43.479
It's a data question.

00:32:43.479 --> 00:32:44.270
AUDIENCE: Religion.

00:32:44.270 --> 00:32:45.145
DAN ARIELY: Religion?

00:32:45.145 --> 00:32:45.692
No.

00:32:45.692 --> 00:32:49.497
AUDIENCE: Well, the practices
of getting [INAUDIBLE].

00:32:49.497 --> 00:32:51.080
DAN ARIELY: The
practices-- oh, so you

00:32:51.080 --> 00:32:53.770
think it's about the ratio
