00:39:20.170 --> 00:39:24.180
more than this number, and
there's never equal number.

00:39:24.180 --> 00:39:25.922
And it takes a
little bit of time,

00:39:25.922 --> 00:39:27.130
but the market solves itself.

00:39:27.130 --> 00:39:30.830
But of course, at any point in
time, you know if you're alone,

00:39:30.830 --> 00:39:33.995
and you see who else is there,
