00:39:46.520 --> 00:39:50.150
So if we have loyalty.

00:39:50.150 --> 00:39:52.280
If somebody pairs
up with somebody,

00:39:52.280 --> 00:39:54.850
and even if they could
have somebody better,

00:39:54.850 --> 00:39:58.370
they don't want to switch, this
creates friction in the system.

00:39:58.370 --> 00:40:01.940
So every time there's friction
for either reasons of loyalty

00:40:01.940 --> 00:40:06.040
or lack of information and so
on, the effect will be less.

00:40:06.040 --> 00:40:07.680
But it doesn't mean
it will go away.

00:40:07.680 --> 00:40:10.109
It would just be
a smaller effect.

00:40:10.109 --> 00:40:11.900
