accounts were actually faked.

00:53:27.490 --> 00:53:29.170
They were basically
just employees

00:53:29.170 --> 00:53:32.380
of the company that were
talking to men as-- I mean,

00:53:32.380 --> 00:53:35.460
it fits with your
thesis of conversation.

00:53:35.460 --> 00:53:39.670
But I'm wondering, do you
think the trend still holds?

00:53:39.670 --> 00:53:42.154
Or is it just that all
these female accounts

