00:53:53.500 --> 00:53:56.130
Our estimation of how
many accounts were fake

00:53:56.130 --> 00:53:58.670
was very different than
what other people had.

00:53:58.670 --> 00:54:01.160
But we looked at
active accounts that I

00:54:01.160 --> 00:54:05.270
don't think people made up.

00:54:05.270 --> 00:54:06.980
We also had
geographic variation.

00:54:06.980 --> 00:54:09.280
So we could tell
you by zip code.

00:54:09.280 --> 00:54:10.930
So we could tell
you that Palo Alto

00:54:10.930 --> 00:54:13.499
